      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EMRITES (7) had been in the money in recent times without winning, then turned things around at her latest appearance over 1800m at this track, scoring by 5.5 metres after being up on the pace. Interesting to see what unfolds from this wide draw. Won't find this any harder, and she can make it two on the trot. LOCHINVAR RULER (4) is in good form with top-five finishes at his last four starts, most recently recording a second over 1800m at this track. Perfectly placed and is sure to be there at the finish again. NEDS BEACH NZ (3) can make the most of this draw, and he is worth another chance after a last-start eighth over 1790m at Mildura nine days ago. REACT TO BEAUTY (1) cops the pole position, and she should be thereabouts at the finish. Include.",
